card.name: Blue-Eyes White Dragon
card.description: This legendary dragon is a powerful engine of destruction. Virtually invincible, very few have faced this awesome creature and lived to tell the tale.

card.name: Red-Eyes B. Dragon
card.description: A ferocious dragon with a deadly attack.

card.name: Summoned Skull
card.description: A fiend with dark powers for confusing the enemy. Among the Fiend-Type monsters, this monster boasts considerable force.(This card is always treated as an "Archfiend" card.)

card.name: Celtic Guardian
card.description: An elf who learned to wield a sword, he baffles enemies with lightning-swift attacks.

card.name: Gyakutenno Megami
card.description: This fairy uses her mystical power to protect the weak and provide spiritual support.

card.name: Buster Blader
card.description: Gains 500 ATK for each Dragon monster your opponent controls or is in their GY.

card.name: Jinzo
card.description: Trap Cards, and their effects on the field, cannot be activated. Negate all Trap effects on the field.

card.name: Shiba-Warrior Taro
card.description: This card cannot be destroyed by battle. When a card on the field is destroyed by battle or by a card effect, return this face-up card to its owner's hand.
